e></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 29, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ypz1665702565044.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ypz1665702565044.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ypz1665702565044.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ypz1665702565044\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ypz1665702565044___name_308026\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get or set the name of a Struct member, as it is known to its parent.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__topic_d94295e1_d94296e1_d94297e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__p_d94298e1_d94299e1_d94300e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-&gt;$name</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__topic_d62767e1_d62768e1_d62769e1_d62770e1_d62771e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1137482e68\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10391e1_d10392e1_d10393e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Return Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10391e1_d10392e1_d10393e1__entry__1\">Return Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10391e1_d10392e1_d10393e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10391e1_d10392e1_d10393e1__entry__1\">\"\"</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10391e1_d10392e1_d10393e1__entry__2\">Struct has no name, or\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct</var> does not refer to a Struct</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10391e1_d10392e1_d10393e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">StructName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10391e1_d10392e1_d10393e1__entry__2\">Name of the Struct</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Struct Functions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__2\">Error Constant</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__3\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-84</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">UACTERR_NO_OBJECT</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__3\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Struct</var> refers to zero\n                     Structs</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1151</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USTRUCTERR_NO_COMMON_CHARACTERISTICS</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__3\">Collection of Structs that do not share a\n\t\t\t\t common parent or the specified characteristic</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1157</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">USTRUCTERR_ILLEGAL_MEMBER_TYPE</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ypz1665702565044__table_d10394e1_d10395e1_d10396e1__entry__3\">Not a valid Struct member type</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__topic_d62772e1_d62773e1_d62774e1_d62775e1_d62776e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1137482e208\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__p_d94307e1_d94308e1_d94309e1\">Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$name</span> to get the name of a\n            single Struct member, or assign a name to a Struct. The function also works on a\n            collection of Structs, but only if they all have the same name and the same parent.\n            Otherwise, an error is returned.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__section_ahj_stx_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1137482e220\">Creating a Named Struct</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ypz1665702565044__pre_bhj_stx_wwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">function createStruct\n variables\n struct vStruct\n endvariables\n ; Create a Struct named ORDER\n vStruct-&gt;$name = \"ORDER\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xhv1665702565119.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Example: Using Special Characters and Reserved Words as Member Names</a><p>To enable member names to include spaces, special characters, or reserve names, use quotation marks around the member names when assigning them.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617221\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617221\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$name Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 29, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get or set the name of a Struct member, as it is known to its parent. Struct ->$name Return Values Table 1. Return Values Return Value Meaning \"\" Struct has no name, or Struct does not refer to a Struct StructName Name of the Struct Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following Struct Functions Value Error Constant Meaning -84 UACTERR_NO_OBJECT Struct refers to zero Structs -1151 USTRUCTERR_NO_COMMON_CHARACTERISTICS Collection of Structs that do not share a common parent or the specified characteristic -1157 USTRUCTERR_ILLEGAL_MEMBER_TYPE Not a valid Struct member type Description Use $name to get the name of a single Struct member, or assign a name to a Struct. The function also works on a collection of Structs, but only if they all have the same name and the same parent. Otherwise, an error is returned. Creating a Named Struct function createStruct variables struct vStruct endvariables ; Create a Struct named ORDER vStruct->$name = \"ORDER\" end Copy Related Links Example: Using Special Characters and Reserved Words as Member Names To enable member names to include spaces, special characters, or reserve names, use quotation marks around the member names when assigning them. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}